sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant HTTPServer as HTTP Server (FastAPI)<br/>8080/TCP<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant GRPCServer as gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant PredictSvc as GlobalPredictServicer
    participant TrainSvc as GlobalTrainServicer
    participant ModelMgr as ModelManager
    participant LoadedModel as LoadedModel<br/>(Module.run)
    participant ModelMesh as Model Mesh Controller<br/>Unix Socket / 8085/TCP
    participant MRSvc as ModelRuntimeServicer
    participant Loader as CoreModelLoader
    participant S3 as S3 / Filesystem
    participant OTEL as OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8086/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 1: HTTP Model Inference
    Client->>HTTPServer: POST /api/v1/{task}/...<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    HTTPServer->>PredictSvc: Route to servicer<br/>(Python in-process)
    PredictSvc->>ModelMgr: Retrieve loaded model
    ModelMgr->>LoadedModel: Module.run(request)
    LoadedModel-->>ModelMgr: Prediction result
    ModelMgr-->>PredictSvc: Result
    PredictSvc-->>HTTPServer: Response
    HTTPServer-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(or SSE stream)

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 2: gRPC Model Inference
    Client->>GRPCServer: {TaskName}Service RPC<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS/mTLS
    GRPCServer->>PredictSvc: CaikitRuntimeServerWrapper<br/>routes dynamic RPC
    PredictSvc->>ModelMgr: Retrieve loaded model
    ModelMgr->>LoadedModel: Module.run(request)
    LoadedModel-->>ModelMgr: Prediction result
    ModelMgr-->>PredictSvc: Result
    PredictSvc-->>GRPCServer: Response
    GRPCServer-->>Client: gRPC Response<br/>(unary or server-stream)

    Note over ModelMesh, S3: Flow 3: Model Loading via Model Mesh
    ModelMesh->>MRSvc: loadModel(modelId, modelPath)<br/>gRPC via Unix socket
    MRSvc->>ModelMgr: load_model(model_id, path)
    ModelMgr->>Loader: CoreModelLoader.load()
    Loader->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, IAM Auth
    S3-->>Loader: Model files
    Loader-->>ModelMgr: Loaded module instance
    ModelMgr-->>MRSvc: Load complete
    MRSvc-->>ModelMesh: LoadModelResponse(sizeInBytes)

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 4: Training Job
    Client->>HTTPServer: POST /api/v1/{module}/train<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, multipart form
    HTTPServer->>TrainSvc: Route to train servicer
    TrainSvc->>LoadedModel: Module.train(data) [async]
    LoadedModel->>S3: Read training data<br/>HTTPS/443 (S3Files plugin)
    S3-->>LoadedModel: Training data
    LoadedModel->>S3: Save trained model<br/>Local filesystem / S3
    Client->>HTTPServer: GET /api/v1/training/status<br/>Poll for completion
    HTTPServer-->>Client: TrainingStatus response

    Note over HTTPServer, Prom: Observability
    HTTPServer->>OTEL: Push traces<br/>gRPC/4317 or HTTP/4318<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    GRPCServer->>OTEL: Push traces<br/>gRPC/4317 or HTTP/4318
    Prom->>HTTPServer: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086 plaintext
